{"tid":2447292,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"赤燭網路商店正式上線 『返校』『還願』DRM free","createTime":"2021-03-15T05:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T03:41:54.000Z","uid":261873,"like":110,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b5e9002d4d42b44eeb07a2b8c8e0dcb4268f96","tid":2447292,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:58:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/redcandlegames/posts/2571321839836428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fredcandlegames%2Fposts%2F2571321839836428&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=72e546ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/redcandlegames/posts/2571321839836428</a><br />\n<br />\n大家好，我們是赤燭<br />\n新的一年，新的嘗試<br />\n在此向大家報告<br />\n赤燭網路商店正式上線了<br />\n<a href=\"https://shop.redcandlegames.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.redcandlegames.com%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=64d3c7b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.redcandlegames.com/</a><br />\n從今以後，赤燭團隊所創作的遊戲產品<br />\n如現有的『返校』、『還願』，以及未來的所有專案<br />\n都將會在赤燭網路商店上架販售（PC、Mac、Linux平台限定）<br />\n遊戲商品皆為 DRM free ，遊玩時無需網路連線、賬號驗證<br />\n衷心希望能為所有陪伴赤燭至今的朋友們提供一個更加單純、便利的購買管道<br />\n目前商品的內容還遠遠算不上豐富，功能也在持續完善中<br />\n假如您在使用中遇到問題，或想到了任何建議<br />\n都歡迎透過網路商店專用信箱與我們聯絡<br />\nshop-support@redcandlegames.com<br />\n再次感謝大家這段時間以來的關心<br />\n2021年，我們將繼續努力，也請多多指教<br />\n赤燭遊戲<br />\n<br />\ngog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知有無習近平小熊維尼"},{"pid":"f63c21b69fa80c6fa280339b1c1319f47e6caca1","tid":2447292,"uid":22898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時有新作"},{"pid"